<ENAMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">One</ENAMEX> was so fantastic in appearance , it was dubbed Hallucigenia .
Would that Mr. <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Gould</ENAMEX> 's minute descriptions of these creatures was always so colorful .
A good deal of the book is boring , particularly the endless allusions to high and pop culture and the frequent jokes festooning the text .
